# .cursorrules - Om Apex MCP Server

## Project Overview

**Path:** `/Users/nishad/om-apex/tools/mcp-server/`
**GitHub:** https://github.com/om-apex/tool-mcp-server
**Company:** Om Apex Holdings LLC
**Tech Stack:** Python 3.10+ / MCP SDK / Supabase / Google Calendar API

This is the Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that provides persistent memory across all Claude interfaces (Chat, Cowork, Claude Code). It stores business context, decisions, tasks, and generates branded documents.

