## MCP Tools Available

### Reading Tools
- `get_full_context` - Load all context at session start
- `get_company_context` - Company structure
- `get_technology_decisions` - Tech stack decisions
- `get_decisions_history` - All recorded decisions
- `get_domain_inventory` - Domain list
- `get_pending_tasks` - Task list
- `get_daily_progress` - Session logs
- `list_calendar_events` - Google Calendar

### Writing Tools
- `add_decision` - Record a decision
- `add_task` / `complete_task` / `update_task` - Task management
- `add_daily_progress` - Log session progress
- `generate_branded_html` - Create branded documents
- `create_calendar_event` / `delete_calendar_event` - Calendar management

---

