## Local Development Ports (TECH-092)

All Om Apex projects have dedicated ports:

| Project | Port | URL |
|---------|------|-----|
| AI Quorum | 3000 | http://localhost:3000 |
| Owner Portal | 3001 | http://localhost:3001 |
| AI Solutions | 3002 | http://localhost:3002 |
| Supply Chain | 3003 | http://localhost:3003 |
| Luxe Properties | 3004 | http://localhost:3004 |

**Note:** MCP server runs via Claude Desktop stdio, not HTTP ports.

---

## Development Commands

```bash
# Install in development mode
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest tests/

# Run linting
ruff check src/

# Start server locally (for testing)
python -m om_apex_mcp.server
```

---

## Git Sync Protocol (CRITICAL)

This repo is edited from BOTH laptops (Nishad's Mac and Sumedha's Windows).

**Before making changes:**
```bash
git pull origin main
```

**After making changes:**
```bash
git add -A && git commit -m "Description" && git push origin main
```

